Cell["\<\
which I will not take the trouble to do; I don't off-hand see the utility of \
such a result, and anyway I have already established the point I wanted to \
make\[Ellipsis]which is that the lop-sided nature of Richard's transformation \
tends to throw things out of kilter.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.54653307742867*^9, 3.546533085687846*^9}, {
  3.546533194819481*^9, 3.546533330727317*^9}}],

